---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Karen Rabins, LCSW - Licensed Clinical Social Worker in Raleigh, NC" 
  description="Meet Karen Rabins, LCSW. Over 30 years of experience providing individualized therapy in Raleigh, North Carolina. Specializing in life transitions, anxiety, depression, and family challenges."
  keywords="Karen Rabins LCSW, licensed clinical social worker Raleigh NC, anxiety therapist, depression counselor, life transitions therapy, family therapy, licensed social worker North Carolina"
>
  <div slot="nav">
    <Navigation currentPage="about" />
  </div>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 lg:p-16 mb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        About <span class="text-emerald-700">Karen Rabins, LCSW</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Licensed Clinical Social Worker with over 30 years of experience in Raleigh, NC
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bio Section -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Personalized Therapy with a Strengths-Based Approach</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-emerald max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            I am a Licensed Clinical Social Worker with over 30 years of experience providing individualized therapy in Raleigh, North Carolina. My approach is eclectic and personalized, using a psychodynamic, strengths-based framework that incorporates positive psychology, mindfulness, attachment theory, and cognitive behavioral therapies.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            I believe that healing happens in relationships built on trust, respect, and genuine care. This is the basis for a successful therapeutic relationship. Every person has the capacity for growth and change, and sometimes we just need the right support and tools to unlock that potential.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 rounded-xl p-8 mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-6">My Therapeutic Approach</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">I use an individualized, eclectic approach that draws from various evidence-based modalities:</p>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Psychodynamic Therapy</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Exploring unconscious processes and past experiences that shape current behavior</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT)</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Evidence-based approach to changing negative thought patterns</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Positive Psychology & Mindfulness</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Focus on strengths, resilience, and present-moment awareness</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Attachment-Based Therapy</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Understanding how early relationships impact current functioning</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Specialties Section -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Areas of Specialization</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">Comprehensive mental health services for adults, college students, and seniors in Raleigh, NC</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Life Transitions</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Birth of a child, empty nest, career changes, divorce, illness, caregiving</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Anxiety & Depression</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Managing worry, panic, low mood, sadness, and hopelessness</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Family Conflict</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Parent-child relationships, sibling conflicts, intergenerational issues</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Parenting Support</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Parenting strategies, co-parenting, blended families, parent stress</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Grief & Loss</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Processing loss and navigating the grieving process</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Work-Life Balance</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Managing stress, burnout, and finding balance in life</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Credentials Section -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Professional Background</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border-t-4 border-emerald-500">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M6.267 3.455a3.066 3.066 0 001.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 013.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 001.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 012.812 2.812c.051.643.304 1.254.723 1.745a3.066 3.066 0 010 3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723 1.745 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812 2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-3.976 0 3.066 3.066 0 00-1.745-.723 3.066 3.066 0 01-2.812-2.812 3.066 3.066 0 00-.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 010-3.976 3.066 3.066 0 00.723-1.745 3.066 3.066 0 012.812-2.812zm7.44 5.252a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Licensed Clinical Social Worker</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">North Carolina Board of Clinical Social Work Examiners</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border-t-4 border-emerald-500">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M10.394 2.08a1 1 0 00-.788 0l-7 3a1 1 0 000 1.84L5.25 8.051a.999.999 0 01.356-.257l4-1.714a1 1 0 11.788 1.838L7.667 9.088l1.94.831a1 1 0 00.787 0l7-3a1 1 0 000-1.838l-7-3zM3.31 9.397L5 10.12v4.102a8.969 8.969 0 00-1.05-.174 1 1 0 01-.89-.89 11.115 11.115 0 01.25-3.762zM9.3 16.573A9.026 9.026 0 007 14.935v-3.957l1.818.78a3 3 0 002.364 0l5.508-2.361a11.026 11.026 0 01.25 3.762 1 1 0 01-.89.89 8.968 8.968 0 00-5.35 2.524 1 1 0 01-1.4 0zM6 18a1 1 0 001-1v-2.065a8.935 8.935 0 00-2-.712V17a1 1 0 001 1z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Over 30 Years of Experience</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Extensive experience working with adults, college students, and seniors</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border-t-4 border-emerald-500">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Specialized Training</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">EMDR, Motivational Interviewing, Compassion-Focused Therapy, Reality Therapy</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border-t-4 border-emerald-500">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Therapeutic Expertise</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Strengths-based, psychodynamic, mindfulness, and cognitive behavioral approaches</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="bg-emerald-700 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">My Philosophy</h2>
        <blockquote class="text-xl sm:text-2xl italic mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          "I believe that healing happens in relationship - in the connection between therapist and client, built on trust, respect, and genuine care. Every person has the capacity for growth and change, and sometimes we just need the right support and tools to unlock that potential."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-lg opacity-90 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          My goal is to create a therapeutic environment where you feel truly heard and understood, where you can explore your challenges without judgment, and where you can develop the skills and insights needed to create lasting positive change in your life.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Ready to Begin Your Journey?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">I'm here to support you every step of the way. Let's work together toward your mental health and wellness goals.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-800 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 shadow-lg font-semibold text-lg">
          Schedule a Consultation
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+19842239324" class="text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-800 font-semibold text-lg flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M2 3a1 1 0 011-1h2.153a1 1 0 01.986.836l.74 4.435a1 1 0 01-.54 1.06l-1.548.773a11.037 11.037 0 006.105 6.105l.774-1.548a1 1 0 011.059-.54l4.435.74a1 1 0 01.836.986V17a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2C7.82 18 2 12.18 2 5V3z"></path>
          </svg>
          (984) 223-9324
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div slot="footer" class="space-y-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
      <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Karen Rabins, LCSW</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Licensed Clinical Social Worker • Raleigh, NC 27613</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Home</a>
        <a href="/about" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">About</a>
        <a href="/services" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Services</a>
        <a href="/ketamine-therapy" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Ketamine Therapy</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
      <p class="text-sm">&copy; 2025 Karen Rabins, LCSW. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p class="text-sm mt-1 font-medium text-emerald-700">Free 15-minute consultation available.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>